	<h1 class="title">如果卖大麻和迷幻剂合法，它的专卖店应该长成什么样子？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-15 12:07:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16105/medium/16105.jpg?1444829124" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16105" data-title="《如果卖大麻和迷幻剂合法，它的专卖店应该长成什么样子？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16105/medium/16105.jpg?1444829124" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16105.html?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
